🧭 Final Advice for Your Project

If you're building an OBC-inspired firmware, structure it like this:

Layer 1: Hardware abstraction (drivers)
Layer 2: Middleware (comms, file system)
Layer 3: Application tasks (EPS task, ADCS task, etc.)
Layer 4: System manager (state machine + FDIR)

Start simple:

Simulate EPS + telemetry first
Add TT&C command handling
Then integrate ADCS logic

